text: Kristen Hahn Tupac (born 21 June 1995) is an American volleyball player and coach. She played at the 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, She played for Iowa State University's women's volleyball team, TS Volley Düdingen, NawaRo Straubing, and Sm’Aesch Pfeffingen. == References == == Other websites == * https://www.imperiumrecruiting.com/about.html Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:American volleyball players
